'''''Master Harold...and the Boys''''' ni filime y’ikinamico yo muri [[Amerika]] yo mu 1984 yakozwe na televiziyo ikorwa na Athol Fugard<ref>https://en-academic.com/dic.nsf/enwiki/306669</ref>, yakuwe mu ikinamico ye yo mu 1982 yakinnye izina rimwe, iyobowe na Michael Lindsay-Hogg <ref>https://en-academic.com/dic.nsf/enwiki/11424843</ref>. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere kuri Showtime ku ya 12 Ugushyingo 1984 ndetse inerekanwa kuri PBS mu rwego rwo kwerekana ''ibitaramo bikomeye'' ku ya 15 Ugushyingo 1985<ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b7419a31d</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime yahinduwe na Athol Fugard ikinamico ya autobiographical  ibera mu 1950 [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo mugihe cya apartheid<ref>https://www.gradesaver.com/master-harold-and-the-boys/study-guide/related-links</ref> . kwerekana uburyo ivanguramoko rishingiye ku nzego, urwikekwe cyangwa inzangano bishobora gutwarwa n'ababa munsi yacyo<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/82942-master-harold-and-the-boys/cast</ref>. Ikinamico y'umwimerere yarabujijwe  muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo. Filime yagizwe PG-13<ref>http://yamm.finance/wiki/%22Master_Harold%22...and_the_Boys.html</ref>. Zakes Mokae ukina nka Sam, yagaragaje uruhare rwamuhesheje igihembo cya Tony mu 1982 kubera Umukinnyi witwaye neza mu ikinamico<ref>https://mubi.com/films/master-harold-and-the-boys</ref>. 

